<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="rigid-adj">rigid <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'rɪdʒɪd/    美 /'rɪdʒɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>坚硬的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a rigid bar of metal 
坚固的金属横杆</p></div>

<h4 id="2-inflexible">2.<strong>固执的；刻板的 (inflexible)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>rigid attitudes 
固执的态度</p></div></div>